'''苏珊·格林菲尔德'''（{{lang-en|Susan Greenfield}}，{{bd|1950年|10月1日|}}）是一位[[英国|英国]]科学家和作家<ref name="greenfieldphd">{{cite thesis|degree=DPhil|first=Susan|last=Greenfield|title=Origins of acetylcholinesterase in cerebrospinal fluid|publisher=University of Oxford|date=1977|url=http://solo.bodleian.ox.ac.uk/primo_library/libweb/action/display.do?doc=oxfaleph016961302}}</ref>，[[英國上議院|上議院]]议员<ref name="baroness">{{cite web|url=https://publications.parliament.uk/pa/ld200102/minutes/010626/ldminute.htm|title=Minutes and Order Paper – Minutes of Proceedings|accessdate=27 October 2007|publisher=UK Parliament House of Lords|year=2001|author=House of Lords}}</ref>，主要研究方向是[[帕金森氏症|帕金森氏症]]和[[阿茲海默症|阿茲海默症]]的治疗，以及[[神经科学|神经科学]]的[[意识|意识]]领域<ref>[http://www.susangreenfield.com/about-susan/books#The Private Life of the Brain (2000)], susangreenfield.com; accessed 5 April 2016.</ref>，现代技术对大脑的影响<ref>{{Cite web|title=Screen Technologies|url=http://www.susangreenfield.com/science/screen-technologies|website=susangreenfield.com|accessdate=17 September 2015}}</ref>。

==个人生活==
格林菲尔德1991年与[[牛津大学林肯学院|牛津大学林肯学院]]教授[[彼得·阿特金斯|彼得·阿特金斯]]结婚，2005年离婚<ref name="ind08">{{cite news|first=Cole|last=Moreton|url=https://www.independent.co.uk/news/science/susan-greenfield-the-girl-with-all-the-brains-825916.html|title=Susan Greenfield: The girl with all the brains|newspaper=The Independent on Sunday|date=11 May 2008|location=London, UK|accessdate=16 April 2016}}</ref>。

